    {
      "_id": "zadQdUq4eeiDSHSq",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
      "name": "Shadow Spawn",
      "sort": 700000,
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>When a creature's shadow is pulled free by Steal Shadow, it becomes a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.pathfinder-bestiary.XrmHgbKgcHDi4OnK]{Shadow Spawn} under the command of the shadow that created it. This shadow spawn doesn't have Steal Shadow. If the creature the shadow spawn was pulled from dies, the shadow spawn becomes a full-fledged, autonomous shadow. If the creature recovers from its @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeeblement}, its shadow returns to it and the shadow spawn is extinguished.</p>"
        },
